ggplot2 Cheat Sheet:
Three Variables

library(ggplot2)

Contour Map

seals$z = with(seals, sqrt(delta_long^2 + delta_lat^2))
p = ggplot(seals, aes(long, lat))
p = p + geom_contour(aes(z=z))
print(p)

Raster Map

seals$z = with(seals, sqrt(delta_long^2 + delta_lat^2))
p = ggplot(seals, aes(long, lat))
p = p + geom_raster(aes(fill=z))
print(p)

Tile Map

seals$z = with(seals, sqrt(delta_long^2 + delta_lat^2))
p = ggplot(seals, aes(long, lat))
p = p + geom_tile(aes(fill=z))
print(p)
